      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds okay, but I'm a bit worried about the timing. The actual shipment from the supplier was pushed back by a month, so we won't have anything for a while. If we keep them listed as in stock, aren't we just going to end up with a bunch of backorders and angry customers once they realize they have to wait 30+ days?",
